Quality Plumbing Products and Specialties















More than 3500 plumbing specialty items... 
Welcome to the William H. Harvey Company, today we have more than 3500 plumbing specialty items that are sold throughout North and South America. It would be difficult to find a hardware store that does not stock some products made by the Harvey Company. 135 sales representatives call on over 5,000 plumbing and hardware wholesalers nationally. New items are added every year.
We specialize in the areas of: 

Solvent Cements, Primers & Cleaners
Pipe Thread Sealants & Tapes, Lubricants and Gasket Materials
Wax Toilet Bowl Gaskets and Toilet Installation Kits
Epoxy & Plumbers Putty, Caulks and Sealants
Washing Machine Hoses, Washing Machine Boxes, Sink/Tub/Drain Products
Toilet Repair Parts and Fasteners
Soldering and Abrasive Supplies
Antifreeze, Spa/Hot Tub Chemicals and Hand & Surface Cleaners
Drain Cleaning Chemicals and Tools
Genuine Sloan Valves, Repair Parts and Urinal Screens
Sinks/Tub/Drain Replacement Parts "O" Rings & Faucet Washers
Shower Pan Liner, Plumbing Construction Materials and Tools
Plastic & Corrugated Bin Boxes, Nipple Caddies and Accessories


 
 
